SIMPLE: something
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Something
<hw>Some"thing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Anything unknown, undetermined, or not specifically designated; a
certain indefinite thing; an indeterminate or unknown event; an
unspecified task, work, or thing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There is <qex>something</qex> in the wind.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The whole world has <qex>something</qex> to do,
<qex>something</qex> to talk of, <qex>something</qex> to wish for, and
<qex>something</qex> to be employed about.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Something</qex> attemped, <qex>something</qex> done,⟦br⟧
Has earned a night's repose.</q> <rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A part; a portion, more or less; an indefinite
quantity or degree; a little.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Something</qex> yet of doubt remains.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Something</qex> of it arises from our infant state.</q>
<rj><qau>I. Watts.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A person or thing importance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If a man thinketh himself to be <qex>something</qex>, when he is
nothing, he deceiveth himself.</q> <rj><qau>Gal. vi. 3.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Something</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Something
<hw>Some"thing</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In some degree; somewhat; to
some extent; at some distance.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I <qex>something</qex> fear my father's wrath.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We have <qex>something</qex> fairer play than a reasoner could
have expected formerly.</q> <rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My sense of touch is <qex>something</qex> coarse.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It must be done to-night,⟦br⟧
And <qex>something</qex> from the palace.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sometime</ent>⟦br⟧
